## Next Steps
The new website code is located at `/Users/canerden/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/habitat-website`.
You can run it locally by navigating to that directory and running `npm run dev`.

If you are satisfied with this version, you can deploy it to Vercel or any other hosting provider of your choice!
